trade propos new ec grain intervent rule the european commun ( ec ) cereal trade lobbi organis cocer said it ha written to ec farm commission fran andriessen to propos a new system for sale into intervent , which it claim could save the ec budget money . it propos that applic for intervent be made through a certif valid for execut three month later . if dure the three month the trader found a market elsewher , he could buy back the certif on payment of a one pct premium . cocer argu that thi would restor the origin function of intervent as a safeti net and would end the present situat in which produc is often sold into intervent as a precaut .